1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:04,262
QualCanvas AI features run only when you choose an AI action.

2
00:00:04,262 --> 00:00:08,064
They can suggest codes, draft a summary or help sketch

3
00:00:08,064 --> 00:00:11,867
a framework, but they do not watch the project in

4
00:00:11,867 --> 00:00:14,528
the background or make an interpretation final.

5
00:00:14,928 --> 00:00:18,704
The AI use policy explains the request path.

6
00:00:18,704 --> 00:00:23,424
Relevant prompt and source text are sent through the QualCanvas

7
00:00:23,424 --> 00:00:27,200
backend to the selected provider for that request.

8
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:31,920
QualCanvas records usage metadata, not the prompt or response content.

9
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:35,213
The AI menu keeps each action explicit.

10
00:00:35,213 --> 00:00:39,347
Select only the material needed for the task, review every

11
00:00:39,347 --> 00:00:43,480
suggestion and keep a non-AI workflow when the consent form

12
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:47,200
or ethics approval does not cover external model processing.

13
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:52,085
You can configure a supported provider key in account settings

14
00:00:52,085 --> 00:00:55,224
when your institution prefers direct provider governance.

15
00:00:55,224 --> 00:00:59,708
Keys are encrypted at rest, and the provider relationship still

16
00:00:59,708 --> 00:01:03,296
needs to fit your protocol and data-processing requirements.

17
00:01:03,696 --> 00:01:09,320
Sending an excerpt to a model provider is a data-processing step.

18
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:14,433
Confirm lawful basis, processor terms and participant disclosure before using

19
00:01:14,433 --> 00:01:16,989
AI with real research data.

20
00:01:16,989 --> 00:01:20,568
An available button is not ethical permission.

21
00:01:20,968 --> 00:01:25,683
Where the study uses AI, document the provider, model, feature

22
00:01:25,683 --> 00:01:27,569
and human decision process.

23
00:01:27,569 --> 00:01:32,285
QualCanvas can export an AI disclosure record, but you should

24
00:01:32,285 --> 00:01:37,000
verify that the final methods statement matches the actual study.

25
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:41,833
The safe pattern is minimise what you send, review every

26
00:01:41,833 --> 00:01:46,265
result, document the assistance and remain accountable for the interpretation.

27
00:01:46,265 --> 00:01:51,584
Visit qualcanvas dot com slash trust slash AI for the current policy.
